,"file_path":"/ef9dYKxDe2isgNhoJsGrt9yjXPz.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/cwsBDxvFn0pkxPOrQg8Koz2kMRM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/wH70cPulVex1eTrLMMJiba5RQAP.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/4Bf6GtNUpBk4bGfNcsVCtS4yhKp.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/34t3lZNaeg0kblry3oYFFD0X8Js.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/uaSIzbRfwLidxRNMvdZAUwW3vtL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/2C3CdVzINUm5Cm1lrbT2uiRstwX.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.714},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ya9TFSMHcCMvhgnmZh26mKY5MJL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/xxcybNaW4oHyhBHMA4ppU8K45ET.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":2293,"height":1290,"file_path":"/yyqcKExb3QX2ozEnGMC1V91dBKN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/iUaaacUrTT58zkeBdeR1iMrhCF.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/8DM2fFEiK0XeZEDu11oiCVI348O.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/mCj7npY8lTpsUgpYGocGIZjGue0.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T14:09:09.597+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Based on the most well-known classical fantasy novel of China, Fengshenyanyi, the trilogy is a magnificent eastern high fantasy epic that recreates the prolonged mythical wars between humans, immortals and monsters, which happened more than three thousand years ago."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"封神第一部：朝歌风云","runtime":148,"tagline":"看黄b片网：4488𝟺𝟔𝟵.com","homepage":"","overview":"天寒地冻，杀气逼人。大商二王子殷寿带领亲手调教的质子旅和殷商大军征讨叛乱的冀州侯苏护，却无意间解除了轩辕坟中妖狐的封印。妖狐附身苏护之女妲己的身上，被殷寿带回朝歌献给父王和王兄。夜宴之上，大王子智乱神迷，拔剑弑父。在此之后，殷寿继承王位，而天降灾异又迫使他做出自焚祭天的决定。与此同时，昆仑仙人姜子牙携封神榜下山，寻找天下共主，以期救拔苍生。在朝歌期间，他觉察到殷寿的残暴，遂匆匆逃离。另一方面，曾视殷寿为明主的王子殷郊以及西伯侯质子姬发也发现了商王的私欲和妲己的诡异之处。阴云密布的朝歌，即将掀起一场血雨腥风……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Phong Thần Đệ Nhất Bộ: Triều Ca Phong Vân","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nội dung phim bắt đầu khi đất nước phải đối mặt với hàng loạt hiện tượng kỳ lạ mà trời đất bất ngờ trừng phạt. Trước tình thế đó, Khương Tử Nha quyết định rời khỏi núi Côn Luân và mang theo Bảng Phong Thần đến chỗ Thương Vương Ân Thọ để giải cứu chúng sinh khỏi cảnh lầm than. Khương Tử Nha không biết rằng ngọn nguồn của mọi tai họa đều đến từ sự thông đồng giữa Thương vương Ân Thọ, yêu hồ Đát Kỷ và Thân Công Báo. Điều này tạo nên một cuộc đối đầu gay go và quyết liệt giữa cái thiện và cái ác. Thương vương Ân Thọ đã trở thành một đại ác nhân. Trong khi đó, Thân Công Báo sở hữu võ công cao cường, có khả năng tách đầu ra khỏi cơ thể, tạo ra mối nguy hiểm lớn cho Khương Tử Nha và đồng đội."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"봉신연의: 조가풍운","runtime":0,"tagline":"거대한 전쟁의 서막이 열린다!","homepage":"","overview":"반란군과의 전쟁에서 승리한 왕자 은수. 절세미인 달기와 부왕을 죽이고 왕좌에 오른다. 천륜을 저버린 만행과 폭정에 하늘이 노하고 원시천존은 천벌이 내려진 인간들을 구할 ‘봉신방’을 강지아에게 주어 인간계로 보낸다. 사대백후를 제거한 은수에게 마계가 동참하고 마침내 신계, 인간계, 마계의 전쟁이 불타오르는데… 장대한 판타지 액션 대서사시를 만난다"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"封神第一部","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《魔戒三部曲》金牌監製巴里奧斯本擔任顧問，天價特技打造奇幻視覺盛宴狂掃24億票房，改編自兩大古典巨著《封神演義》及《武王伐紂平話》又一影像絢麗神作——大商二王子殷壽（費翔 飾）帶領親手調教的質子旅和大軍出征叛亂的冀州侯蘇護，意外解除了妖狐的封印並附身於蘇護之女妲己（娜然 飾），被殷壽帶回朝歌。夜宴之上，大王子智亂神迷，拔劍弒父。殷壽即殺兄並繼承王位，卻引致天譴降臨；此時，崑崙仙人姜子牙（黃渤 飾）攜「封神榜」下凡，尋找天下共主，以期拯救蒼生，卻覺察到殷壽的兇狠殘暴而遲疑；曾視父王為明主的王子殷郊（陳牧馳 飾）以及西伯侯姬昌（李雪健 飾）之子、質子姬發（于適 飾）也發現了商王的私慾和妲己的詭秘異常，決定背叛殷壽，終於掀起封神世界的風雲變幻…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I : Kingdom of Storms","runtime":149,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Royaume de Chine, dans l'Antiquité. Déterminé à monter sur le trône, le prince Yin Shou finit par atteindre son objectif en éliminant des membres de sa propre famille. Régnant en véritable tyran, il s'attire rapidement les foudres de nombreux ennemis qui souhaitent le voir payer pour ses méfaits…"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"封神第一部：朝歌風雲","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"大商二王子殷壽（費翔 飾）帶領親手調教的質子旅和殷商大軍徵討叛亂的冀州侯蘇護，卻無意間解除了軒轅墳中妖狐的封印。妖狐附身蘇護之女妲己（娜然 飾）的身上，被殷壽帶回朝歌獻給父王和王兄。夜宴之上，大王子智亂神迷，拔劍弒父。在此之後，殷壽繼承王位，而天降災異迫使他做出自焚祭天的決定。同時，崑崙仙人薑子牙（黃渤 飾）攜封神榜下山，尋找天下共主，以期救拔蒼生。朝歌期間，他覺察到殷壽的殘暴，遂匆匆逃離。另一方面，曾視殷壽為明主的王子殷郊（陳牧馳 飾）以及西伯侯質子姬發（於適 飾）也發現了商王的私慾和妲己的詭異之處。  陰雲密布的朝歌，即將掀起一場血雨腥風…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Стварање богова I: Краљевство олуја","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Заснована на најпознатијем класичном фантазијском роману Кине, трилогија је величанствени источњачки високофантастични еп који реконструише дуготрајне митске ратове између људи, бесмртника и чудовишта, који су се десили пре више од три хиљаде година."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gebaseerd op de meest bekende klassieke fantasy-roman van China, Fengshenyanyi, de trilogie is een prachtig oost-high fantasy epos, dat nauwkeurig de langdurige mythische oorlogen tussen mensen, immortals en monsters, die er gebeurd meer dan drie duizend jaar geleden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"အမြီး ၉ ချောင်းမြေခွေးဖြစ်တဲ့ စူးတာကျိမိဖုရားနဲ့ ရှန်းဘုရင်တို့ကြောင့် တိုင်းသူပြည်သားတွေ ဒုက္ခရောက်ပြီး လောကတခွင်ကို မိစ္ဆာနတ်ဆိုးတွေနှောက်ယှက်ဖျက်ဆီးနေကြတာကြောင့် နတ်တွေကဝိုင်းဝန်းတားဆီးဖို့ ဖြစ်လာတဲ့အခါ….။ရှေးခေတ်က လူသားတွေ မိစ္ဆာတွေ နတ်ဘုရားတွေကြားက ဒဏ္ဍာရီစစ်ပွဲတွေအကြောင်းကို စိတ်လှုပ်ရှားစွာကြည့်ရှုခံစားရမယ့် ရုပ်ရှင်အလန်းစားစစ်စစ်ကြီးဖြစ်ပါကြောင်း။"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"my","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Burmese"},{"data":{"title":"בריאת האלים הראשון: ממלכת הסערות","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"המבוססת על רומן הפנטזיה הקלאסי הידוע ביותר של סין, Fengshenyanyi, הטרילוגיה היא אפוס פנטזיה מזרחי מפואר המשחזר את המלחמות המיתולוגיות הממושכות בין בני אדם, בני אלמוות ומפלצות, שהתרחשו לפני יותר משלושת אלפים שנה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Трилогия о богах. Часть 1","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"С начала времён миром смертных правила династия Шан, и все местные князья в знак подчинения посылали ко двору своих сыновей. Во время подавления мятежа в одной из провинций младший принц Инь Шоу случайно пробуждает заточённого демона-лису, которая вселяется в тело покончившей с собой дочери мятежного князя. Она потворствует его низменным желаниям — император и его старший сын погибают, Инь Шоу становится правителем, чем навлекает на мир смертных Великое проклятье. Чтобы не допустить хаос, боги горы Куньлунь решают отправить людям артефакт невероятной силы — Список бессмертных, отнести который вызывается Цзян Цзыя в сопровождении Нэчжи и Эрлана."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"آفرینش خدایان ۱: پادشاهی طوفان‌ها","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"این سه گانه بر اساس شناخته شده‌ترین رمان فانتزی کلاسیک چین، Fengshenyanyi (تفویض خدایان)، یک حماسه فانتزی باشکوه شرقی است که جنگ‌های افسانه‌ای متمادی بین انسان‌ها، جاودانه‌ها و هیولاها را که بیش از سه هزار سال پیش رخ داده است، بازسازی می‌کند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"กำเนิดเทพเจ้า 1: อาณาจักรแห่งพายุ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เมื่อใต้หล้าต่างระส่ำระสายภายใต้อำนาจของประมุขทรราชแห่งราชวงศ์ซาง นักพรตเซียนจึงต้องนำม้วนกระดาษศักดิ์สิทธิ์มายังโลกมนุษย์ เพื่อชำระล้างชะตาต้องสาปให้อาณาจักร"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I - Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Basata sul più noto romanzo fantasy classico cinese, Fengshenyanyi, la trilogia è una magnifica epopea orientale high fantasy che ricrea le prolungate guerre mitiche tra umani, immortali e mostri, avvenute più di tremila anni fa."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Criação dos Deuses 1: Reino das Tempestades","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Baseada no mais conhecido romance clássico de fantasia da China, Fengshenyanyi, a trilogia é um magnífico épico de alta fantasia oriental que recria as prolongadas guerras míticas entre humanos, imortais e monstros, ocorridas há mais de três mil anos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Βασισμένη στο πιο γνωστό κλασικό μυθιστόρημα φαντασίας της Κίνας, το Fengshenyanyi, η τριλογία αυτή είναι ένα υπέροχο ανατολίτικο έπος υψηλής φαντασίας που αναδημιουργεί τους παρατεταμένους μυθικούς πολέμους μεταξύ ανθρώπων, αθανάτων και τεράτων, που συνέβησαν πριν από τρεις χιλιάδες χρόνια."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Criação dos Deuses I: Reino das Tempestades","runtime":0,"tagline":"O prelúdio de uma grande guerra começa!","homepage":"","overview":"Baseado no mais conhecido romance clássico de fantasia da China, Fengshenyanyi, a trilogia é um magnífico épico de fantasia oriental que recria as prolongadas guerras míticas entre humanos, imortais e monstros, que aconteceram há mais de três mil anos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Stvaranje Bogova I: Kraljevstvo oluja","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Utemeljena na najpoznatijem klasičnom fantastičnom romanu Kine, Fengshenyanyi, trilogija je veličanstveni istočnjački visokofantastični ep koji rekreira dugotrajne mitske ratove između ljudi, besmrtnika i čudovišta, koji su se dogodili prije više od tri tisuće godina."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Stvarjenje bogov I: Kraljestvo neviht","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Veličasten vzhodnjaški fantazijski ep, ki temelji na najbolj znanem kitajskem klasičnem fantazijskem romanu Fengshenyanyi. Poustvarja dolgotrajne mitske vojne med ljudmi, nesmrtniki in pošastmi, ki so se zgodile pred več kot tri tisoč leti."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Trilogie vychází z nejznámějšího klasického čínského fantasy románu Fengshenyanyi a je velkolepým východním high fantasy eposem, který rekonstruuje vleklé mýtické války mezi lidmi, nesmrtelnými a netvory, jež se odehrály před více než třemi tisíci lety."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"König Zhou (Kris Phillips), der letzte Herrscher der Shang-Dynastie, wird von einem Geist, der die Gestalt seiner Konkubine annimmt, verhext. Daraufhin wird er zum Tyrannen und es entbrennt ein epischer Kampf, um ihn zu stürzen. Neben Menschen sind daran auch Götter, Dämonen und andere mythische Wesen beteiligt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Narodziny Bogów: Królestwo burz","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Narodziny Bogów: Królestwo burz to kinowe wydarzenie roku z Dalekiego Wschodu. Epicki rozmach. Rekordowy budżet 150 milionów dolarów. Ekranizacja legendy, którą znają miliony ludzi na świecie. Zobacz największą bitwę jaką stoczyła ludzkość 3000 lat temu z Bogami i Demonami, walcząc o przetrwanie na Ziemi."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Çin'in en tanınmış klasik fantastik romanı Fengshenyanyi'den uyarlanan bu üçleme, üç bin yıldan fazla süre önce insanlar, ölümsüzler ve canavarlar arasındaki uzun süren efsanevi savaşları yeniden yaratan muhteşem bir doğu yüksek fantastik destanıdır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"La creación de los dioses: el reino de las tormentas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una epopeya de fantasía oriental que recrea las prolongadas guerras míticas entre humanos, inmortales y monstruos que tuvieron lugar hace más de tres mil años."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"La creación de los dioses: El reino de las tormentas","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una epopeya de fantasía oriental que recrea las prolongadas guerras míticas entre humanos, inmortales y monstruos que tuvieron lugar hace más de tres mil años."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Az Istenek felemelkedése I. - Viharok Birodalma","runtime":0,"tagline":"Elkezdődik egy nagy háború előjátéka!","homepage":"","overview":"Miután összeesküvést szőtt egy álnok rókadémonnal, hogy megölje az apját a királyt és magához ragadja a hatalmat, Yin Shou olyan brutális zsarnokként uralkodik, hogy magára vonja a mennyek haragját. Egy utolsó kísérletként, hogy megmentsék a kétségbeesett halandók világát a pusztulástól, Kunlun halhatatlanjai úgy döntenek, hogy közbelépnek, és egy valószínűtlen bajnokba fektetnek, aki elég bátor ahhoz, hogy kihívja és legyőzze a velejéig romlott királyt - még ha ez mindenébe kerül is."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Creația Zeilor I: Regatul Furtunilor","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bazată pe cel mai cunoscut roman fantasy clasic al Chinei, Fengshenyanyi, trilogia este o epopee magnifică de înaltă fantezie orientală, care recreează războaiele mitice prelungite dintre oameni, nemuritori și monștri, care au avut loc în urmă cu mai bine de trei mii de ani. (sursa: subs.ro)"},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"استنادًا إلى رواية الخيال الكلاسيكي الأكثر شهرة في الصين، Fengshenyanyi، تعد الثلاثية ملحمة شرقية رائعة من الخيال العالي تعيد خلق الحروب الأسطورية الطويلة بين البشر والخالدين والوحوش، والتي حدثت منذ أكثر من ثلاثة آلاف عام."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"La creació dels déus: el regne de les tempestes","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"El tirànic rei Zhou i la seva consort, l'esperit de guineu Su Daji, desfermen la ira del Cel. Els savis de la muntanya Kunlun, en percebre el caos, envien Jiang Ziya per trobar el sobirà legítim i restaurar l'ordre. Mentrestant, el príncep Ji Fa, criat sota la tutela del rei Zhou, descobreix la seva crueltat i fuig de la capital Chaoge. Amb l'ajuda de Jiang Ziya, lidera una rebel·lió per enderrocar el tirà."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En klassisk Wuxia Fantasy i modern tappning, som handlar om ett krig mellan de odödliga, människorna och monstren som levde tillsammans för 3000 år sen i Kina."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6533970a42d83700c93eaabb","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6533970a42d83700c93eaabb","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2023-10-21T09:16:58.504Z","updated_at":"2023-10-21T09:16:58.641Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"672cf01fcaf727f3748a9f94","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/672cf01fcaf727f3748a9f94","author":"Sejian","content":"This was quite fun!\r\n\r\n\"The Investiture of the Gods, also known by its Chinese names Fengshen Yanyi and Fengshen Bang, is a 16th-century Chinese novel and one of the major vernacular Chinese works in the gods and demons genre written during the Ming dynasty.\" Yes please, give me more!\r\n\r\nThis is the second time this year I'm being treated with the mother goddess Nuwa in media, and being mixed Chinese and only recently learning this part of Chinese mythology, I am happy for it!\r\n\r\nIt's a long movie, so strap in. I don't complain about movie length unless it's a snore and this isn't. The CGI isn't perfect and it can \"feel\" off sometimes but it's fine.\r\n\r\nI ain't got much else to say. Enjoy!","created_at":"2024-11-07T16:51:43.916Z","updated_at":"2024-11-07T16:51:43.941Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"Sejian","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":479753,"adult":false,"title":"Shockwave: Countdown to Disaster","video":false,"overview":"A stolen seismic weapon is activated in Yemen. A hostage freed there tries in vain to warn against its global effect. It starts seismic activity at the Californian fault line where her daughter and ex are monitoring it. Can they stop it?","genre_ids":[28,878,12,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1765,"vote_count":107,"poster_path":"/sBD608VF4TcFHmP7SuC0OcvZQ0b.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-02","vote_average":5.509,"backdrop_path":"/mIpdOcss3oedSYB8juiSXg89uLL.jpg","original_title":"Shockwave: Countdown to Disaster","original_language":"en"},{"id":1026563,"adult":false,"title":"13 Exorcisms","video":false,"overview":"After participating in a séance, young Laura begins to behave strangely. Alarmed, her parents ask Father Olmedo, one of the few exorcists authorized by the Vatican to intervene in cases of demonic possession, for help.","genre_ids":[18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9319,"vote_count":186,"poster_path":"/kdaEAPrT3Dq7pPjdhfTgNyMeOnK.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-04","vote_average":5.895,"backdrop_path":"/rvFeNpYimvtEEZgkhiBfXJA5oTf.jpg","original_title":"13 exorcismos","original_language":"es"},{"id":50146,"adult":false,"title":"The Golden Lotus","video":false,"overview":"Golden Lotus is based, in part, on Jin Ping Mei, a famous erotic novel of ancient China. Li Han-Hsiang adapted part of the story into this film, which starts with Hsi Men Ching, a successful merchant, wooing Pan Chin Lien, the beautiful wife of one of the townspeople.","genre_ids":[10749,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5307,"vote_count":68,"poster_path":"/woB42KiNtESKv9O0h5yOYBYzm0m.jpg","release_date":"1974-01-17","vote_average":7.037,"backdrop_path":"/787qS8sM6IpEAJCfggKid0E7ZZo.jpg","original_title":"金瓶雙艷","original_language":"zh"},{"id":683361,"adult":false,"title":"Super Furball Saves the Future","video":false,"overview":"To save the world, Super Furball has to save the bees. In order to do so, the heroic guinea pig has to redeem the biggest bully in school.","genre_ids":[10751,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5671,"vote_count":53,"poster_path":"/cYQhEjz8TcycbHpf9qHBxroYE0M.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-14","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/1kD7E6soGxkNoWrKKniVnrkHNAH.jpg","original_title":"Supermarsu 2","original_language":"fi"},{"id":1108211,"adult":false,"title":"Lost in the Stars","video":false,"overview":"He Fei's wife, Li Muzi, disappears during their anniversary trip. When she reappears, he insists that she is not his wife. As Chen Mai, a top lawyer gets involved in this bizarre case, more mysteries start to emerge.","genre_ids":[9648,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3151,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/88zdJKhD42Mpnd3if4RXYyILT9P.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-22","vote_average":6.575,"backdrop_path":"/T6MfrCWpEyDOpbNqILFT6MHxb3.jpg","original_title":"消失的她","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1107387,"adult":false,"title":"Hachiko","video":false,"overview":"This is the story of a puppy that touched hundreds of millions of people around the world. Hachiko is a cute Chinese pastoral dog. He met his destined owner Chen Jingxiu in the vast crowd and became a member of the Chen family. With the passage of time, the once beautiful home is no longer there, but Batong is still waiting where it is, and its fate is closely tied to its family.","genre_ids":[18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3739,"vote_count":270,"poster_path":"/whY9rKS8p9Iw2fR2HTF7JAOTcr5.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-31","vote_average":7.935,"backdrop_path":"/sptxlzXJA1t1oWrtAv3t88cKkB2.jpg","original_title":"忠犬八公","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1155281,"adult":false,"title":"Creation of the Gods II: Demon Force","video":false,"overview":"Taishi Wen Zhong led the army of Shang Dynasty including Deng Chanyu and four generals of the Mo Family to Xiqi. With the help of Kunlun immortals such as Jiang Ziya, Ji Fa led the army and civilians of Xiqi to defend their homeland.","genre_ids":[28,14,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.6133,"vote_count":128,"poster_path":"/dfUCs5HNtGu4fofh83uiE2Qcy3v.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":6.371,"backdrop_path":"/yujcZMkNKtNXPvRGyTA3e3VCrbx.jpg","original_title":"封神第二部：战火西岐","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1146972,"adult":false,"title":"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED FREEDOM","video":false,"overview":"In C.E.75, the fighting still continues. There are independence movements, and aggression by Blue Cosmos... In order to calm the situation, a global peace monitoring agency called COMPASS is established, with Lacus as its first president. As members of COMPASS, Kira and his comrades intervene into various regional battles. Then a newly established nation called Foundation proposes a joint operation against a Blue Cosmos stronghold.","genre_ids":[16,878,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.888,"vote_count":73,"poster_path":"/1EBnttleJaKnWWyyEqfiSn76ZjT.jpg","release_date":"2024-01-26","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/fU3oaBud5SZadw6k1ycftYedmXJ.jpg","original_title":"機動戦士ガンダムSEED FREEDOM","original_language":"ja"},{"id":876792,"adult":false,"title":"That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime the Movie: Scarlet Bond","video":false,"overview":"A long-running conspiracy is swirling over a mysterious power wielded by the Queen in Raja, a small country west of Tempest. When a slime who evolved into a Demon Lord named Rimuru Tempest crosses paths with Hiiro, a survivor of the Ogre race, an incredible adventure packed with new characters begins. The power of bonds will be put to the test!","genre_ids":[16,14,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.828,"vote_count":422,"poster_path":"/xITip9n9uMAUA0TU6niMXU2tbh0.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-25","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/g03h9TULzJZOoXA34Abp5LE7lvt.jpg","original_title":"劇場版 転生したらスライムだった件 紅蓮の絆編","original_language":"ja"},{"id":857553,"adult":false,"title":"Johnny & Clyde","video":false,"overview":"Johnny and Clyde are two serial killers who are madly in love and on an endless crime spree. Alana (Megan Fox) is the confident and cunning owner of a prosperous casino that generates tens of millions of dollars each year. Johnny and Clyde decide to assemble a ragtag group of criminals and misfits to steal from Alana's casino and pull off the heist of the century. Unfortunately for Johnny and Clyde's crew, Alana has a deadly weapon at her disposal – the monstrous slasher spirit known as Bakwas.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0788,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/cdfdR90WYCTQmYoQ0aDRZP8I2IL.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-23","vote_average":4.9,"backdrop_path":"/5S6502vFWcJCu8jyAEBXgT8nDxo.jpg","original_title":"Johnny & Clyde","original_language":"en"},{"id":913521,"adult":false,"title":"Sisi & I","video":false,"overview":"After an elaborate application process, Empress Elisabeth of Austria hires Countess Irma as her new lady-in-waiting and takes her to her summer residence on Corfu. As the two women become closer there, this soon leads to tensions back in Vienna.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5859,"vote_count":52,"poster_path":"/6J61mawQOGhYXXuKGuZrsiqC7fV.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-30","vote_average":6.202,"backdrop_path":"/rXQwZuQe8GZhSSuAPFVVKZsyPvh.jpg","original_title":"Sisi & Ich","original_language":"de"},{"id":1027604,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Cursed in Time: Alchemist's Quest","video":false,"overview":"It follows young alchemist Amélie as she acquires a magical power: partially influencing the flow of time. But she is split in time, and Amélie from the present meets Améliw from the past, who accompanies her every step of the way.","genre_ids":[10751,14,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0513,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/ywzbF5YSBfZ7XqcGO9YR6Gy4VFt.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-17","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/rNP32TLwnUky6uuUyCIDatGCd6x.jpg","original_title":"Princezna zakletá v čase 2","original_language":"cs"},{"id":813079,"adult":false,"title":"Don't Buy the Seller","video":false,"overview":"Soo-hyun, who has recently moved into a new house, buys a used washing machine through a second-hand app but finds out it doesn't work. Annoyed by the seller's irresponsibility, she leaves a comment calling the seller a con man, and reports it to the police. Little does she know that the seller is a psychopathic serial killer who uses an online second-hand market to lure his victims. Her comment renders his hunt for a new victim all but impossible so she becomes his next target. She starts receiving obscene phone calls, countless unwanted food deliveries, and strange men knocking on her door looking for a good time. A trip to the sender's address proves deadly serious when the police and Soo-hyun find a man’s dead body.","genre_ids":[53,9648,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2688,"vote_count":81,"poster_path":"/kYmoJSypfpB9OnwvxebiV1nZUXi.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-30","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/elqCaVi6Amkx5hzPsJ3Km5Ru3Yg.jpg","original_title":"타겟","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1300182,"adult":false,"title":"Juanpis González: The People's President","video":false,"overview":"When a spoiled Colombian snob becomes president through money and connections, he finds staying in power takes more than he expected.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2428,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/zK0Xw1EIbIqLSLyYZDUz36rswzv.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-27","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/v5Sh1essBJ6204gv8BsKWE33wVT.jpg","original_title":"Juanpis González: El presidente de la gente","original_language":"es"},{"id":1150906,"adult":false,"title":"Bullets and Katanas","video":false,"overview":"How would you react if you were a Martial Arts expert, had a Katana in your hands, and your daughter had just been kidnapped. Under this premise, Sensei Marín launches a race against time with Nacho, his best friend.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0964,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/oAQxlli6yUg0mGqLxaFhr8oX4H7.jpg","release_date":"2023-05-26","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/8ilV2iB8VU11tXwXnLJLGvMvzOS.jpg","original_title":"Balas y Katanas","original_language":"es"},{"id":661579,"adult":false,"title":"Under the Light","video":false,"overview":"Officers Su Jianming and Li Huilin investigate a crime involving wealthy businessman Li Zhitian. As clues emerge, the investigation becomes more and more like a game of chess.","genre_ids":[18,28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7728,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/gESv9WPvbmbOwO50vT6yF2OuWwF.jpg","release_date":"2023-09-28","vote_average":5.782,"backdrop_path":"/9tOJfyyvBY0jUYk5pYC7Jgq06zX.jpg","original_title":"坚如磐石","original_language":"zh"},{"id":494892,"adult":false,"title":"God","video":false,"overview":"A psych-drama-thriller combo that tackles shady politicians, leaked documents and a lack of enthusiasm for religion.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1809,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/4np8KzfT7XHgwQT5sJTRogqIn0s.jpg","release_date":"2016-12-29","vote_average":8.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"God","original_language":"en"},{"id":1080512,"adult":false,"title":"Pandemonium","video":false,"overview":"Nathan and Daniel are caught in a road accident that kills them both. As they come to grips with their deaths, Nathan confronts his past and the consequences of his actions. Now trapped in the hellish void of Pandemonium, he encounters tortured souls like Jeanne, a disturbed child; Julia, a grief-stricken mother; and Norghul, the guide of the great void. Will he find a way to escape the torment that awaits him for eternity?","genre_ids":[27,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6019,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/TQ4WcuSgwdSdM7DtBKQdjBDGOZ.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-25","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/HLNprTMU4dZeroXmSBbgdzt6f6.jpg","original_title":"Pandemonium","original_language":"fr"},{"id":977246,"adult":false,"title":"Sorcery","video":false,"overview":"Chiloé Island, 1880. Rosa Raín is a Huilliche girl who, after the murder of her father at the hands of German settlers, seeks justice with Mateo, leader of an organization of sorcerers called “La Recta Provincia”.","genre_ids":[27,9648,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3677,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/oGNJSxvLqvbHEYfKnR2Mmx3pY7E.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-14","vote_average":6.25,"backdrop_path":"/ro9Vo81Q8lwCj3T15Qd4vpDPnru.jpg","original_title":"Brujería","original_language":"es"},{"id":1135229,"adult":false,"title":"I Am Rage","video":false,"overview":"An ancient cult embroiled in a sinister blood trade makes the deadly mistake of abducting a young woman with a violent, shocking past.","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3921,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/tnsioPDTf5qXWFIkMvFc1HtKaHz.jpg","release_date":"2023-09-14","vote_average":6.768,"backdrop_path":"/dcZ8QpzVBRKPdYM6lPTucd2hFJM.jpg","original_title":"I Am Rage","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":5147,"adult":false,"title":"The Lost Continent","video":false,"overview":"An eclectic group of characters set sail on Captain Lansen’s leaky cargo ship in an attempt to escape their various troubles. When a violent storm strikes, the ship is swept into the Sargasso Sea and the passengers find themselves trapped on an island populated by man-eating seaweed, giant crabs and Spanish conquistadors who believe it’s still the 16th century.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":0.5524,"vote_count":52,"poster_path":"/tlEUe4DyZ21j4pApjF6nT8EYZAj.jpg","release_date":"1968-06-19","vote_average":5.549,"backdrop_path":"/zK03Kjo6ltX3D8PWbtfTusk0nDX.jpg","original_title":"The Lost Continent","original_language":"en"},{"id":5491,"adult":false,"title":"Battlefield Earth","video":false,"overview":"In the year 3000, man is no match for the Psychlos, a greedy, manipulative race of aliens on a quest for ultimate profit. Led by the powerful Terl, the Psychlos are stripping Earth clean of its natural resources, using the broken remnants of humanity as slaves. What is left of the human race has descended into a near primitive state. After being captured, it is up to Tyler to save mankind.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":1.441,"vote_count":914,"poster_path":"/wXCRuBHdJ5aTFQdsuGJFXNdo79T.jpg","release_date":"2000-05-12","vote_average":3.323,"backdrop_path":"/hqJfW8G8FL28rckFHuCoKPecpG9.jpg","original_title":"Battlefield Earth","original_language":"en"},{"id":5470,"adult":false,"title":"Beowulf","video":false,"overview":"Beowulf is a wanderer who learns about a man-eating creature called Grendel, which comes in the night to devour warriors trapped at the Outpost. The Outpost is ruled by Hrothgar. He has a daughter, whose husband may have been murdered by the Outpost's master of arms.","genre_ids":[12,14,28,27],"popularity":0.8572,"vote_count":243,"poster_path":"/ktX5naCHfERaoDVaCUOITPIFrFd.jpg","release_date":"1999-03-31","vote_average":4.348,"backdrop_path":"/9bdTdaqxT2ZEVGZwXsMvG7410cT.jpg","original_title":"Beowulf","original_language":"en"},{"id":5471,"adult":false,"title":"Beowulf & Grendel","video":false,"overview":"The blood-soaked tale of a Norse warrior's battle against the great and murderous troll, Grendel. Heads will roll. Out of allegiance to the King Hrothgar, the much respected Lord of the Danes, Beowulf leads a troop of warriors across the sea to rid a village of the marauding monster.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,14],"popularity":0.8435,"vote_count":245,"poster_path":"/49s4KMmF2YBJhHYTqwdvikpTztt.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-14","vote_average":5.545,"backdrop_path":"/jSaZ02GsGuFIGo0B2kh3FA7hQ0Y.jpg","original_title":"Beowulf & Grendel","original_language":"en"},{"id":859010,"adult":false,"title":"Super Sentai Strongest Battle Director's Cut","video":false,"overview":"A mysterious girl named Rita gathers heroes from Super Sentai teams to the planet Nemesis. The heroes are told that any wish they desire will come true if they can win the \"Super Sentai Strongest Battle\" tournament.  A director's cut of the mini-series as a full-length feature.","genre_ids":[28,878,9648,18],"popularity":0.604,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/oPeCo68dPgqPUdE2uO9KGswxMdT.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-10","vote_average":9,"backdrop_path":"/lT8DO9MgnbTgQ7CnlMoawDUnje3.jpg","original_title":"スーパー戦隊最強バトル！！ ディレクターズカット版","original_language":"ja"},{"id":9078,"adult":false,"title":"The Sword in the Stone","video":false,"overview":"Wart is a young boy who aspires to be a knight's squire. On a hunting trip he falls in on Merlin, a powerful but amnesiac wizard who has plans for him beyond mere squiredom. He starts by trying to give him an education, believing that once one has an education, one can go anywhere. Needless to say, it doesn't quite work out that way.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":4.3437,"vote_count":4046,"poster_path":"/7lyeeuhGAJSNXYEW34S8mJ1bwI8.jpg","release_date":"1963-12-25","vote_average":7.22,"backdrop_path":"/m1TOfgljbT3jOez3b4l1I1tm82W.jpg","original_title":"The Sword in the Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":9104,"adult":false,"title":"Buffalo Soldiers","video":false,"overview":"A criminal subculture operates among U.S. soldiers stationed in West Germany just before the fall of the Berlin wall.","genre_ids":[18,35,10752,80,53],"popularity":4.6762,"vote_count":344,"poster_path":"/qNl4T8xxC0xDeX8JFJVCBzH4Kg8.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":6.281,"backdrop_path":"/7Pw5NOv7aUtmHyh1yASEldOlAz0.jpg","original_title":"Buffalo Soldiers","original_language":"en"},{"id":9278,"adult":false,"title":"Freejack","video":false,"overview":"Time-traveling bounty hunters find a doomed race-car driver in the past and bring him to 2009 New York, where his mind will be replaced with that of a terminally ill billionaire.","genre_ids":[878,28,80,18],"popularity":3.0128,"vote_count":347,"poster_path":"/lSN8lIX90Az0t1qvIXC4MlCvd9a.jpg","release_date":"1992-01-17","vote_average":5.46,"backdrop_path":"/8FlHUvNOSANeo8Y8adBNJanEib.jpg","original_title":"Freejack","original_language":"en"},{"id":8966,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight","video":false,"overview":"When Bella Swan moves to a small town in the Pacific Northwest, she falls in love with Edward Cullen, a mysterious classmate who reveals himself to be a 108-year-old vampire. Despite Edward's repeated cautions, Bella can't stay away from him, a fatal move that endangers her own life.","genre_ids":[14,18,10749],"popularity":15.1619,"vote_count":14225,"poster_path":"/3Gkb6jm6962ADUPaCBqzz9CTbn9.jpg","release_date":"2008-11-20","vote_average":6.282,"backdrop_path":"/weAYfu6FfrNxEDJ3xH1XpgQcqUv.jpg","original_title":"Twilight","original_language":"en"},{"id":8974,"adult":false,"title":"The War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"The residents of a small town are excited when a flaming meteor lands in the hills, until they discover it is the first of many transport devices from Mars bringing an army of invaders invincible to any man-made weapon, even the atomic bomb.","genre_ids":[878,28],"popularity":2.5092,"vote_count":680,"poster_path":"/gzc75Za4ArqfXIIr7STNnIE5rnA.jpg","release_date":"1953-04-03","vote_average":6.803,"backdrop_path":"/74Q8M90Tg2TsV3iKjoDpJ77WPMJ.jpg","original_title":"The War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":659993,"adult":false,"title":"Mother at War","video":false,"overview":"1918. World War I rages in Europe while Erna Jensen tends to her ordinary life at home in Bramstrup, with her simple-minded son, Kalle. One day the village constable comes to enlist Kalle for military service for the German Empire – of which Southern Jutland is a part. If Erna is to save Kalle from certain death, she must follow him through thick and thin. Upon a chance meeting with a deserting solder she trades identities. Now disguised as Private Julius Rasmussen, Erna heads for the front. In her encounters with the other soldiers and in the presence of the war, unknown sides of Erna are awoken. This is the story of a woman who won’t let a war prevent her from fighting for what she loves.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":0.4564,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/prrpF81RKedPlx6GIrVkZJ7xPR8.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-29","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/bFm8SF33iEoUQ2sHZZwHbN3D2yl.jpg","original_title":"Erna i krig","original_language":"da"},{"id":660046,"adult":false,"title":"Ponniyin Selvan: Part I","video":false,"overview":"The Chola kingdom is under threat from forces both internal and external, and with crown prince Aaditha Karikalan, his younger brother Arunmozhi Varman and the emperor, Sundara Cholar separated by situations, it is up to a messenger to ensure the safety of the kingdom. Can he succeed in his mission, especially with Karikalan's former girlfriend, Nandhini, plotting to bring down the entire Chola empire?","genre_ids":[28,12,36],"popularity":0.8162,"vote_count":89,"poster_path":"/zSNyZUeqDdii0doQ9970E90kCkb.jpg","release_date":"2022-09-30","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/nrVpYaBw0kqm2ySiwbxo33LnRkr.jpg","original_title":"பொன்னியின் செல்வன்: பாகம் 1","original_language":"ta"},{"id":9061,"adult":false,"title":"Just Cause","video":false,"overview":"A Harvard professor is lured back into the courtroom after twenty-five years to take the case of a young black man condemned to death for the horrific murder of a child.","genre_ids":[28,18,9648,53],"popularity":1.4623,"vote_count":608,"poster_path":"/hbkS4UpgHcGhLlGy9YCX4WIJ4lu.jpg","release_date":"1995-02-17","vote_average":6.266,"backdrop_path":"/i9opFwOh2DvFyjy8uQXC17UEUzL.jpg","original_title":"Just Cause","original_language":"en"},{"id":9297,"adult":false,"title":"Monster House","video":false,"overview":"Monsters under the bed are scary enough, but what happens when an entire house is out to get you? Three teens aim to find out when they go up against a decrepit neighboring home and unlock its frightening secrets.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,14],"popularity":5.8295,"vote_count":4256,"poster_path":"/zCRPr4bkO3ae0U1134vJ39xZnAG.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-30","vote_average":6.707,"backdrop_path":"/3otAGduCHdqdEIVC1HOOLb5Qnp2.jpg","original_title":"Monster House","original_language":"en"},{"id":9300,"adult":false,"title":"Orlando","video":false,"overview":"England, 1600. Queen Elizabeth I promises Orlando, a young nobleman obsessed with poetry, that she will grant him land and fortune if he agrees to satisfy a very particular request.","genre_ids":[18,14],"popularity":1.6775,"vote_count":370,"poster_path":"/seRawEs8eQ8rWfkBm6QC39EQEAU.jpg","release_date":"1992-12-11","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/AoMYwa8yRvXcbRKdD5s8VwIN3NA.jpg","original_title":"Orlando","original_language":"en"},{"id":9007,"adult":false,"title":"Just Like Heaven","video":false,"overview":"Shortly after David Abbott moves into his new San Francisco digs, he has an unwelcome visitor on his hands: winsome Elizabeth Masterson, who asserts that the apartment is hers -- and promptly vanishes. When she starts appearing and disappearing at will, David thinks she's a ghost, while Elizabeth is convinced she's alive.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749,14],"popularity":2.9026,"vote_count":2522,"poster_path":"/2cLbyVNhEEaUJGg7rfbLtX6454I.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-16","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/k63j5qexRlpD3wxzETKfuZRVWiT.jpg","original_title":"Just Like Heaven","original_language":"en"},{"id":9016,"adult":false,"title":"Treasure Planet","video":false,"overview":"When space galleon cabin boy Jim Hawkins discovers a map to an intergalactic \"loot of a thousand worlds,\" a cyborg cook named John Silver teaches him to battle supernovas and space storms on their journey to find treasure.","genre_ids":[878,12,16,10751,14],"popularity":5.888,"vote_count":4515,"poster_path":"/kNhZkR3UNbXfvESQo7mJpOi4tGd.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-26","vote_average":7.565,"backdrop_path":"/f2opsSUSiMdEp6AiY2sbC8QPd8S.jpg","original_title":"Treasure Planet","original_language":"en"},{"id":660273,"adult":false,"title":"Rintamalotta","video":false,"overview":"Irma has been sent to the front immediately after her marriage to Erik Vuori. Irma and her new \"Lotta\" companions find themselves in many dangerous situations during the fighting of the Continuation War. Irma is also concerned about Erik's loyalty.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":2.5044,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/y2XWy9GIrSn0tkAdGhQRMPUmqHe.jpg","release_date":"1956-11-02","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Rintamalotta","original_language":"fi"},{"id":277952,"adult":false,"title":"Padayottam","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by 'The Count of Monte Cristo', Padayottam was the first Indian movie to be shot in 70mm format. Prince Udayan (Nazir) is the successor to the Kolathiri kingdom. He is betrayed by his cousin Devan (Madhu) which forces him to go into exile. Years later Udayan returns to Kolathiri to take his revenge.","genre_ids":[28,18],"popularity":0.2911,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/guaQmiy4vyewBylEPMwQX9Q3v8D.jpg","release_date":"1982-08-06","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/zQZ87ZLp17q8Wk7eXa3u0ij2lsD.jpg","original_title":"പടയോട്ടം","original_language":"ml"},{"id":8871,"adult":false,"title":"How the Grinch Stole Christmas","video":false,"overview":"The Grinch decides to rob Whoville of Christmas - but a dash of kindness from little Cindy Lou Who and her family may be enough to melt his heart...","genre_ids":[10751,35,14],"popularity":7.1169,"vote_count":8163,"poster_path":"/1WZbbPApEivA421gCOluuzMMKCk.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-17","vote_average":6.784,"backdrop_path":"/sy0vo1cmpKqwPRiMUiJ45jyLsX7.jpg","original_title":"How the Grinch Stole Christmas","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt6979756","twitter_id":"FengshenTrilogy","facebook_id":"CreationoftheGods","wikidata_id":"Q67936237","instagram_id":"creationofthegods","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/creation_of_the_gods_i_kingdom_of_storms"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"FengshenTril